<h1>Articles</h1>

Our blog has <%= Article.public_count %> articles and counting! Test basic Rails auth with rick:secret for login! Isn't rails fun?

<ul>
  <% @articles.each do |article| %>
    <% unless article.archived? %>
      <li>
        <%= link_to article.title, article %>
      </li>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
</ul>

